title: Son of a Boy Dad Ep. 65 - She Gone (ft. Pat Stay)
description:
Battle rap legend Pat Stay joins the show to talk about his battle rap days with Rone, The Nicest shoot from this past weekend, why people become lawyers instead of doctors, life in Nova Scotia, and much more funny stuff. Enjoy.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/sonofaboydad
